description_ar:
Experience the epitome of luxury living in Dubai Marina with this fully upgraded 1-bedroom apartment in Botanica Tower 1, presented by Coldwell Banker.


Apartment Highlights:

  • Spacious size of 830.22 sqft
  • Upgraded interiors
  • Mesmerizing sea views
  • Fully furnished for your convenience
  • Optional inclusion of bills
  • Direct access to the vibrant Marina Walk

Step into this exceptional residence, where you'll be greeted by a generous living space offering panoramic sea views that will leave you captivated. With meticulous attention to detail, the apartment has been fully upgraded to enhance your comfort and style. It comes fully furnished, providing you with a hassle-free move-in experience. Additionally, the option to include bills offers further convenience and peace of mind.

Botanica Tower is renowned for its exclusive feature—the tropical sky garden located on the 27th floor, offering a serene and lush oasis within the heart of the city. This prestigious tower effortlessly combines glamour and comfort, providing residents with a truly exceptional living experience.

Amenities:

  • Well-equipped gymnasium for your fitness needs
  • Temperature-controlled swimming pool
  • Invigorating jacuzzi and sauna
  • Barbeque area for outdoor gatherings
  • Pet-friendly environment
  • Direct access to the vibrant Marina Walk, filled with an array of dining and entertainment options
  • Walking distance to Jumeirah Beach Residence (JBR) and The Beach, where pristine shores and leisure activities await

Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this remarkable apartment in Botanica Tower 1. Contact me today to arrange a viewing and secure your luxurious Dubai Marina lifestyle.


Company name: Coldwell Banker

RERA ORN: 1201 

Address: Office 2804, Citadel Tower, Business Bay, Dubai 

Office phone no: +971 (4) 4391200

Office fax no: +971 (4) 4391299

Primary email: info@coldwellbanker.ae

Website: www.coldwellbanker.
